              "free_text": [
                "A beam of 85A MeV 40Ar nuclei, provided by the K1200",
                "cyclotron at the National Superconducting Cyclotron",
                "Laboratory, impinged on a 376 mg/cm2 Be target",
                "located at the production target position of the",
                "A1200 fragment separator. After collimating the beam,",
                "the final beam intensity was around 3 x 10**4 particles",
                "per second and purity was higher that 99%"
